FB Prophet Analysis of the company¶

In [ ]:
df_prophet = df_yf.reset_index().rename(columns={'Date': 'ds', 'Adj Close': 'y'})

# Convert the date column to datetime if it's not already
df_prophet['ds'] = pd.to_datetime(df_prophet['ds'])

# Initialize the Prophet model
model = Prophet()

# Fit the model with your DataFrame
model.fit(df_prophet)

# Create a DataFrame for future predictions
# Here, predicting for the next 30 days
future = model.make_future_dataframe(periods=30)

# Make predictions
forecast = model.predict(future)

# Plot the forecast
model.plot(forecast)
plt.title('Stock Price Forecast for TSLA')
plt.xlabel('Date')
plt.ylabel('Price')
plt.show()

# Plot the forecast components
model.plot_components(forecast)
plt.show()
